name: Cheese-E Expedition
description:
BRIEFING

Gouda-1 your mission is to fly to the distant moon of Cheese-E. There you will find a rock ripe with shapely cheeses. Gather this cheese. Try not to die and good luck!

Created during the Godot Wild Jam #48 under the theme, "Moon."

Wild Card Used:

• "Been Here Before..." - Force the player to return to a previous zone.
